0.0.4:
  - Install RVM, Ruby and gems on puppet server for running spec tests
  - Add progress messages to provisioning scripts
  - Let provisioning scripts abort on errors
  - Add support for CentOS 6 and CentOS 7 clients

0.0.3:
  - Add configuration option for Puppet server version
  - Add configuration options for Puppet agent versions
  - Install PuppetDB and Puppetboard on the puppet master
  - Fix time synchronization issue on VMs

0.0.2:
  - Use vagrant-env for configuration
  - Add support for Ubuntu 18.04 LTS (bionic) client VM
  - Change default client VM box to ubuntu/bionic64

0.0.1:
  initial version
